k\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">10</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Full Directory</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">11</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Owner &amp; Franchise</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">12</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">FAQs</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">13</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">More Resources</span></button></li></ul></nav><div class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-actions\"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-action-btn toc-action-top\"><i class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 bi bi-arrow-up\"></i>Back to Top</button><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-action-btn\"><i class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 bi bi-arrow-down\"></i>To Bottom</button></div></div></div><main class=\"city-page-layout\"><div class=\"mobile-toc-button\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"mobile-toc-trigger\"><i class=\"bi bi-list-ul\"></i><span>Contents</span></button></div><section id=\"city-hero\" class=\"city-hero-section \"><div class=\"section-shell city-hero-shell\"><div class=\"city-hero-copy\"><div class=\"hero-breadcrumbs\"><a href=\"/\">Home</a><i class=\"bi bi-chevron-right\"></i><span>Dog Parks Directory</span><i class=\"bi bi-chevron-right\"></i><strong>Indian Trail</strong></div><p class=\"hero-eyebrow\">Suburban Sanctuary</p><h1>Crossing Paths</h1><div class=\"hero-chip-row\"><div class=\"hero-chip\"><span class=\"chip-label\">Dog Parks</span><span class=\"chip-value\">1</span></div><div class=\"hero-chip\"><span class=\"chip-label\">Events</span><span class=\"chip-value\">Weekly</span></div></div><p class=\"hero-description\">Indian Trail lives up to its motto of &quot;Crossing Paths&quot; by creating spaces where community meets. Crooked Creek Park is a regional destination for dog owners.</p><div class=\"city-rich-description\"><p class=\"rich-description-paragraph\">Indian Trail, North Carolina, has transformed from a bedroom community into a vibrant suburban town with a strong focus on quality of life. At the forefront of this transformation for dog owners is <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"rich-link\" href=\"https://www.indiantrail.org/241/Crooked-Creek-Park\">Crooked Creek Park</a>. This premier facility is more than just a park; it is a recreational destination. The dog park within is spacious, well-equipped with agility obstacles, and serves as a social meeting ground for the community. Surrounding the dog park are miles of paved trails that offer a safe, smooth surface for strollers and dog walkers alike.</p><p class=\"rich-description-paragraph\">The town’s &quot;Crossing Paths Park&quot; serves as the venue for numerous community festivals and events, many of which welcome leashed pets. This integration of dogs into the social fabric of the town makes Indian Trail feel welcoming and inclusive. The parks are characterized by their modern design and safety features, reflecting the town’s commitment to its growing families. For residents, Indian Trail offers the perfect convenience of suburban living with <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"rich-link\" href=\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\">high-quality amenities</a> that rival larger cities.</p></div><div class=\"hero-cta-row\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"hero-cta primary\"><i class=\"bi bi-list-check\"></i>Browse directory</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"hero-cta ghost\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i>Open map</button><a class=\"hero-cta text-link\" href=\"/list-your-park\"><i class=\"bi bi-plus-circle\"></i>Submit a park</a></div><div class=\"hero-footnotes\"><span><i class=\"bi bi-sparkles\"></i> <!-- -->Crooked Creek Park</span><span><i class=\"bi bi-sparkles\"></i> <!-- -->Chestnut Square</span><span><i class=\"bi bi-sparkles\"></i> <!-- -->Crossing Paths Park</span></div></div><div class=\"city-hero-visual\"><div class=\"hero-image-card\"><img alt=\"Indian Trail dog park landscape\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"/images/cities/indian-trail-nc/hero.png\"/><div class=\"hero-image-gradient\"></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"city-premium-section\" aria-labelledby=\"city-premium-heading\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"city-premium-header\"><div><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Premium spotlight</span><h2 id=\"city-premium-heading\">Premium parks in <!-- -->Indian Trail</h2><p>Partners highlighted here are currently investing in featured placement across this guide.</p></div><div class=\"city-premium-header-actions\"><a class=\"hero-cta primary\" href=\"/list-your-park\">Feature my park</a><a class=\"hero-cta ghost\" href=\"/contact\">Talk to sales</a></div></div><div class=\"city-premium-values\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-card\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-megaphone\"></i></div><h4>Pinned above free listings</h4><p>Premium partners appear before every other card within the city directory.</p></div><div class=\"city-premium-value-card\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-envelope-paper\"></i></div><h4>Lead-friendly CTAs</h4><p>Direct website + phone buttons encourage bookings straight from this page.</p></div><div class=\"city-premium-value-card\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-clock-history\"></i></div><h4>Always-on exposure</h4><p>Featured cards show even when we haven’t processed new static data yet.</p></div></div><div class=\"city-premium-grid\"><div class=\"city-premium-card animate-pulse\"><div class=\"city-premium-media bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"h-4 w-1/2 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-2 h-3 w-3/4 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-4 h-16 rounded bg-slate-100\"></div></div><div class=\"city-premium-card animate-pulse\"><div class=\"city-premium-media bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"h-4 w-1/2 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-2 h-3 w-3/4 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-4 h-16 rounded bg-slate-100\"></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"city-insights\" class=\"city-insights-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><section id=\"city-statistics\" class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db city-stats-unified\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stats-section-header\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stats-eyebrow\">City Statistics</span><h2 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db\">How <!-- -->Indian Trail<!-- --> stacks up for dog families</h2><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stats-intro\">Indian Trail has mastered the suburban park experience. Facilities are modern, clean, and designed for families that include four-legged members.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stats-row\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stat-card accent\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-tag\">Top Pick</span><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-value\">Crooked Creek Park</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-copy\">A massive recreational complex with a dedicated dog park, agility features, and miles of paved walking loops.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stat-card \"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-tag\">Central</span><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-value\">Crossing Paths Park</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-copy\">The heart of town events. While more for leashed social walks during festivals, it is the community hub.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stat-card \"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-tag\">Active</span><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-value\">Chestnut Square</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-copy\">Another great recreational facility offering sports fields and walking paths for active outings.</p></div></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db data-grid-container\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db key-metrics-grid\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-item primary\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-icon\"><i class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db bi bi-geo-alt-fill\"></i></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-details\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-number\">16</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-label\">Total Dog Parks</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-sub\">All types combined</span></div></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-item\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-icon\"><i class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db bi bi-star-fill\"></i></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-details\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-number\">4.6</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-label\">Average Rating</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-sub\">Based on <!-- -->2,114<!-- --> reviews</span></div></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-item\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-icon\"><i class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db bi bi-chat-heart-fill\"></i></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-details\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-number\">2,114</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-label\">Total Reviews</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-sub\">Community feedback</span></div></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-item\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-icon\"><i class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db bi bi-trophy-fill\"></i></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-details\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-number\">13</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-label\">Premium Parks</span><span class=\"jsx-9f